name: Tangle 02: Circumstances
description: Trial after trial will always coexist with men's lives. Even though it's only for a moment, it feels endless. Not infrequently we also feel the problem that comes not only one, but it feels like this situation is a variety of problems inflicted on men. But believe me there will be a rainbow at the end of the storm, there will be happiness at the end of trouble. And reassured men, that problems always come with ease.
